| Component | ESP32 Pin Connection | Function |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **HX711 Load Cell Amplifier** | DT -> GPIO 25, SCK -> GPIO 26 | Measures bowl food weight precisely in grams |
| **MG996R Servo Motor** | PWM -> GPIO 18 | Physically controls the food dispenser lid |
| **16x2 I2C LCD Display** | SDA -> GPIO 21, SCL -> GPIO 19 | Displays status codes, Wi-Fi logs, weight, and countdowns |

